          "summary": "Neural Networks: Zero to Hero is a guide to building neural networks from scratch in code. It assumes readers have a solid programming background in Python and know intro-level math. The course covers backpropagation and training, implementing various models, diagnostic tools and visualizations, GPT, and more.",
